    <entry>
      <title>如何在一大堆文件中找到一些内容……</title>
      <link href="/archives/f34b3a09/"/>
      <url>/archives/f34b3a09/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>首先呢，这可能是程序员中的一个常见问题。当然，在一般的项目中，程序员都有个IDE，可以帮助解决一些问题。所以这里说的是基本原理。</p><p>很明显，想要在一堆文件（文件夹）中找到一些内容，首先要做的就是把这些文件列举出来。这里需要运用递归的思想。按照<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%80%92%E5%BD%92">百度百科</a>的说法：程序调用自身的编程技巧称为递归（ recursion）。</p><h1 id="原理"><a href="#原理" class="headerlink" title="原理"></a>原理</h1><p>我们要写的函数叫做<code>list_files(path)</code>，它用来列举出一个文件夹包括子文件夹中的所有文件。并且我们还有两个工具函数：判断一个文件是普通文件还是文件夹的函数<code>isdir(path)</code>，以及列举出一个文件夹下所有文件夹和普通文件的函数叫做<code>listdir(directory)</code>（只列举一层）。</p><p>如果一个文件夹中只有几个普通文件，那么很简单，只要用<code>listdir()</code>就可以了。但是，当这个文件夹中既有普通文件又有文件夹的时候该怎么办呢？</p><p>简单，用<code>list_files()</code>再对查找到的子文件夹调用一次。之后的话，如果查找到文件夹，就再调用一次；如果查找到了普通文件，就直接返回。</p><p>所有的普通文件都收集到一个列表里。</p><p>咋了？还愣着？！正常！看看代码就明白了。</p><h1 id="Python代码"><a href="#Python代码" class="headerlink" title="Python代码"></a>Python代码</h1><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> os <span class="comment"># 引用标准库，内含有isdir()和listdir()</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">list_files</span>(<span class="params">directory</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    files = [] <span class="comment"># 构建一个列表，用于收集查找到的普通文件</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> path <span class="keyword">in</span> os.listdir(directory): <span class="comment"># 列举文件夹下的文件</span></span><br><span class="line">        new_path = os.path.join(directory, path) <span class="comment"># 查找到的新文件路径。os.path.join()可以把文件夹和普通文件（或者是文件夹）合并到一起（毕竟要递归查找，递归总是要有目标的，要朝着目标一步步前进，在这里目标就是找到普通文件）</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> os.path.isdir(new_path): <span class="comment"># 判断是否是文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">            result = list_files(new_path)</span><br><span class="line">            files += result <span class="comment"># 如果结果是列表，那就要合并列表files和结果列表</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            files.append(new_path) <span class="comment"># 如果结果是普通文件，直接把普通文件添加到列表files里就行了</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> files</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当然，最重要的还是拿一个文件夹运行一次试一下，看看结果如何，然后自己再多想想，就能明白递归是怎么回事了。</p><p>至于查找内容，那就是很简单的事情了，为了多少避免一下文不对题的情况，我还是把全部代码贴出来为好：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> os</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> cchardet</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">list_files</span>(<span class="params">directory</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    files = []</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> path <span class="keyword">in</span> os.listdir(directory):</span><br><span class="line">        new_path = os.path.join(directory, path)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> os.path.isdir(new_path):</span><br><span class="line">            result = list_files(new_path)</span><br><span class="line">            files += result</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            files.append(new_path)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> files</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">be_in</span>(<span class="params">filename, content</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(filename, <span class="string">&#x27;rb&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">        original_content = f.read()</span><br><span class="line">        encoding = cchardet.detect(original_content)[<span class="string">&#x27;encoding&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> encoding == <span class="literal">None</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            file_content = original_content.decode(encoding)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> content <span class="keyword">in</span> file_content:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> filename</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">search</span>(<span class="params">path, content</span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    results = []</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> os.path.isdir(path):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> f <span class="keyword">in</span> list_files(path):</span><br><span class="line">            result = be_in(f, content)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> result:</span><br><span class="line">                results.append(result)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> be_in(path, content):</span><br><span class="line">            results.append(path)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> results</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个<code>search()</code>就是用于在一堆文件中查找内容的函数，其余两个函数是工具函数。</p><h1 id="一点题外话"><a href="#一点题外话" class="headerlink" title="一点题外话"></a>一点题外话</h1><p>说到递归，我这里推荐《The Little Schemer》这本书。中文（重印）版tb上有卖。其讲解递归真的很到位，而且也能顺便学习一点Lisp。</p>]]></content>
      
      
