    <entry>
      <title>如何获取常用汉字（GB2312）</title>
      <link href="/archives/d3087bf6/"/>
      <url>/archives/d3087bf6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>听说常用汉字有三千多个，怎么获取呢？其实常用汉字已经有人替我们整理好了，就是字符集GB2312，是我国1980年发布的，共有6763个汉字，分为一级汉字和二级汉字，一级汉字采用拼音排序，二级汉字采用部首排序，一级汉字就是这里说的常用汉字。所以我们只要用一个合适的工具去获取它就行了。这里我们用Python。</p><p>关于GB2312的具体说明可以去<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A2%E7%94%A8%E6%B1%89%E5%AD%97%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E9%9B%86">这里</a>查找。</p><p>先简要说明一下。一个字节（byte）由8个二进制位（bit）组成，所以一个字节可以表示为2<sup>8</sup>=256个整数，范围是0-255。Python的<code>bytes()</code>函数可以把一个整数列表转换成一个字节类型的十六进制数（列表中每个数字都必须大于等于0且小于256）。举个例子：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="built_in">bytes</span>([<span class="number">180</span>, <span class="number">233</span>])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">b&#x27;\xb4\xe9&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># 小提示：Python中可以用hex()函数把一个整数转换成十六进制，来检验一下结果</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>GB2312的编码方式很简单。一个GB2312字符只由两位字节构成。一级汉字中，高位字节的范围是0xB0-0xD7（0x表示十六进制，十进制表示为176-215），低位字节的范围是0xA1-0xFE（十进制表示为161-254；当高位字节为0xF7时，低位字节的范围比这个小，毕竟常用汉字总数才3755个，整除不了256，等下会用粗暴一点的方式解决这个问题）。</p><p>理清了思路，代码就简单了：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> json</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">characters = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">176</span>, <span class="number">216</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> x <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">161</span>, <span class="number">255</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        s = <span class="built_in">bytes</span>([i, x])</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            c = s.decode(<span class="string">&quot;gb2312&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">except</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span></span><br><span class="line">        characters.append(c)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(c, end=<span class="string">&quot;\t&quot;</span>) <span class="comment"># 打印结果</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>() <span class="comment"># 换一行，美观点</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(characters)) <span class="comment"># 打印结果数量</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 保存在一个json文件里</span></span><br><span class="line">filename = <span class="string">&quot;common_chinese_characters.json&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(filename, <span class="string">&quot;w&quot;</span>, encoding=<span class="string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">    json.dump(characters, f, ensure_ascii=<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>说明：<code>bytes.decode(字符集)</code>用于解码，用指定的字符集把字节类型转换为字符类型；<code>str.encode(字符集)</code>用于编码，用指定的字符集把字符类型转换为字节类型。</p><p>代码原理很简单，就是利用for循环去遍历GB2312字符集定义的一级汉字。其中第一个for循环用于遍历高位字节，第二个for循环用于遍历低位字节。<code>try...except...</code>就是刚才说的粗暴一点的方式，用来防止最后几个汉字出错，因为最后一个汉字（座）的GB2312编码表示为0xD7F9，低位字节并非0xFE，但是for循环只会“野蛮地”继续下去，所以只要触发了那个<code>except</code>，就意味着所有字符都已遍历完，也就可以结束了。</p><p><code>json.dump</code>中的<code>ensure_ascii=False</code>是必须的，不信你可以自己试试不用的效果。</p>]]></content>
      
      
